OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe Government has rejected a petition
OL,7,Fsigned by almost 17,000 people calling
OL,8,Ffor a controversial pipeline project
OL,9,Fto be scrapped.
OL,11,FThe #60 million project would
OL,12,Ftransport carbon captured in the Peak
OL,13,FDistrict through Cheshire and the
OL,14,FWirral before being deposited in
OL,15,Fdepleted Morecambe gas fields.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FBut close to 17,000 locals have signed
OL,7,Fa petition calling on the project to
OL,8,Fbe scrapped over worries it could ruin
OL,9,Fthe natural landscapes, harm the local
OL,10,Fwildlife, and pose a potential danger
OL,11,Fto nearby residents.
OL,13,FResponding to the petition on Saturday
OL,14,F7 March, the Government said "there
OL,15,Fare no plans to pause the development
OL,16,Fof UK Offshore CO2 storage projects".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FThe statement went on to say:
OL,7,F"Government works with regulators and
OL,8,Fthe public to ensure CO2 storage
OL,9,Fregulations support the safe
OL,10,Fdeployment of carbon capture and
OL,11,Funderground storage (CCUS).
OL,13,F"The UK does not plan to pause the
OL,14,Fdevelopment of CCUS, as full
OL,15,Findependent safety, environmental and
OL,16,Flegal assessments are already carried
OL,17,Fout for each storage site, and the UK
OL,18,Fhas a strong regulatory environment to
OL,19,Fdeploy CCUS safely."
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FResponding, Councillor Jeff Green,
OL,7,FLeader of Wirral's Conservative
OL,8,FCouncillors, said: "This is an
OL,9,Fappalling response from a Government
OL,10,Fwhich promised, when first elected, to
OL,11,F'listen'.
OL,13,F"It is a knee jerk rejection to the
OL,14,Fviews of so many Wirral residents and
OL,15,Fone which I believe the Labour Party,
OL,16,Fincluding their representatives in
OL,17,FWirral, will come to regret.
OL,19,F"Legitimate fears and concerns for our
OL,20,Fenvironment, eco systems and health
OL,21,Fand wellbeing have been brushed aside.
OL,26,@pD@TOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,F"All of us who are against these plans
OL,7,Fmust now strive even harder to stop
OL,8,FPeak Cluster and secure, I hope,
OL,9,Fanother Government u-turn."
OL,11,FThe Government's decision comes just
OL,12,Fdays before an emergency debate at
OL,13,FWallasey Town Hall on Monday 9 March,
OL,14,Fin which a number of councillors,
OL,15,Fincluding local Labour party members,
OL,16,Fwill call for the project to be paused.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,FCllr Green said the authority's
OL,7,FConservative councillors would also be
OL,8,Fseeking support from all 66
OL,9,Fcouncillors to sign a joint letter to
OL,10,Fthe government requesting the plan is
OL,11,Fhalted.
OL,13,FResponding to local worries over the
OL,14,Fproject, a Department for Energy
OL,15,FSecurity and Net Zero spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid: "Carbon capture, usage and
OL,17,Fstorage is vital for Britain's clean
OL,18,Fenergy future. The Climate Change
OL,19,FCommittee describes it as a 'necessity
OL,20,Fnot an option' for reaching our
OL,21,Fclimate goals.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
