CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772993165
OL,3,CGovernment rejects appeal to scrap
OL,4,Ccontroversial Peak Cluster pipeline
OL,6,F"We are delivering first of a kind
OL,7,Fcarbon capture projects in the UK,
OL,8,Fbacked by #9.4 billion over this
OL,9,Fparliament ` supporting thousands of
OL,10,Fjobs across the country and reigniting
OL,11,Four industrial heartlands."
OL,13,F"All carbon capture projects must meet
OL,14,Fstrict environmental and regulatory
OL,15,Frequirements, including ensuring high
OL,16,Flevels of protection for both
OL,17,Fcommunities and the environment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]uD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
